posting_body: ['Ascend', '26900 242nd Ave SE, Maple Valley, WA, 98038', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 52', 'OR Text', '52', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Live Here, Explore Out There.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 740 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'What is better than living above the clouds in the Pacific Northwest?', 'At our Maple Valley apartments for rent, we take apartment living to the next level.', 'Ascend Maple Valley offers one-, two, and three-bedroom floor plans, as well as an urban one-bedroom floor plan, designed with our residents in mind.', 'Our residents love our community amenities such as our swimming pool, 24-hour fitness center, and our BBQ area.', 'Inside our Maple Valley apartments, you’ll find updated amenities such as quartz countertops, energy efficient appliances, and private balconies/patios.', 'Ascend provides easy access to your weekly desires!', 'Features', '- Energy Efficient Appliances', '- Range Oven', '- Vinyl Plank Flooring', '- Private Patios/Balconies', '- Quartz Countertops', '- Dishwasher', '- Full-Sized Washer & Dryer', '- Disposal', 'Community Amenities', '- Clubhouse and Lounge', '- Free WiFi in Common Areas', '- Playground', '- Package Receiving', '- Dog Park', '- BBQ Area', '- Outdoor Swimming Pool', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', '60 lb.', 'Weight Limit', '2 Pets Maximum', 'Breed Restrictions Apply', '$200 Refundable Deposit per pet', '$200 Non-Refundable Fee per pet', '$25.00 per month Pet Rents', 'GPRvfov1A4g']
